More Information
Declining Phase
The phase of the solar cycle between solar maximum to solar minimum
Domain: Solar
Disk of the Sun
The apparent circular shape of the Sun when seen in the sky, resulting from a two-dimensional projection of a spherical object
Domain: Solar
